				\begin{document}$${\mathrm{V}}_{\mathrm{oc}}=\left|{\mathrm{E}}_{\mathrm{HOMO}}^{\mathrm{donor}}\right|-\left|{\mathrm{E}}_{\mathrm{LUMO}}^{\mathrm{acceptor}}\right|-0.3$$\end{document}

Whilst, in DSSCs, Voc can be approximately obtained as the different energy among LUMO of the dye and conduction band (CB) of the semiconductor3TiO2(ECB=-4.0eV):Voc=ELUMOdye-ECB\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
